OL,3,CProgramme listings for
OL,3,CProgramme listings for SAT 16 MAY
OL,4,G0035FThe Good Old Days
OL,5,     GLeonard Sachs presents the old-
OL,6,     Gtime music hall programme, from
OL,7,     Gthe City Varieties Theatre,
OL,8,     GLeeds. Guests include Ken Dodd,
OL,9,     GBarry Kent, Lyn Kennington, John
OL,10,     GBouchier and Saxburger.
OL,11,G0120FHetty Wainthropp
OL,12,     GWhen Hetty represents her
OL,13,     Gneighbour at a creditor's
OL,14,     Gmeeting, she is hired to find a
OL,15,     Gman who may have stolen from the
OL,16,     Gneighbour.
OL,17,G0210FPersonal Cinema: Maggie Smith
OL,18,     GIn a programme first broadcast in
OL,19,     G1970, Maggie Smith talks to
OL,20,     GMichael Aspel about her career
OL,21,     Gand chooses scenes from some of
OL,22,     Gher favourite films.
